title: The Samsung Galaxy Book Vol 3 Revised Edition - 2014  UK
description:
The Samsung Galaxy Book Vol 3 Revised Edition - 2014  UK

178 Pages | True PDF | English | 17 MB 


The complete independent manual to the latest Samsung Galaxy apps that will help you get more from your device, including the S5. With the latest release of the Samsung Galaxy S5, and the Tab 3, Note 10.1 and Gear pushing the boundaries, there truly is a Samsung device for everyone. This book is suitable for all devices and is filled with guides and tutorials on setting up and customising, and all the essential built-in apps, including Samsung Hubs, Story Album and Samsung Link.
